## üè¢ Departments

### Get All Departments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments

### Get All Departments with Sub-Departments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments?includeSubDepts=true

### Get Single Department
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments/1

### Create Department
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "TEST",
  "name": "Test Department",
  "description": "Test department for API testing",
  "displayOrder": 999,
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Department
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete Department
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/admin/departments/999

